high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then turn left to face the couch.
Pick up the red credit card off of the couch.
Turn around and take a step forward, the turn right and walk over to the chair.
Put the red credit card on the front edge of the seat of the chair.
Turn left and walk towards the door, then hang a left and walk over to the black dresser that the television is on.
Pick up the red credit card off of the dresser.
Turn left and walk forward, then hang a left and walk up to the chair with the red credit card on its seat.
Put the red credit card on the front edge of the seat of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Move two red credit cards to the seat of a chair.

high_descs: Turn around to face the card on the couch.
Pick up the card on the couch.
Turn left to face the arm chair.
Place the card in the arm chair.
Turn around and cross the room to face the card on the TV stand.
Pick up the card on the TV stand.
Turn around and cross the room to face the arm chair.
Place the card in the arm chair.
anns.task_desc: To move two cards to the arm chair to the left of the couch.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the couch.
Pick up the red credit card on the couch.
Bring the card to the chair on the left.
Put the card on the chair.
Turn around move to the TV across the room.
Pick up the red credit card on the TV stand.
Turn around, head back to the chair with the credit card on it.
Put the credit card on the chair, left of the other credit card.
anns.task_desc: Put two credit cards on a chair.
